description:
`SwVersion`: Table storing software version information for Ericsson RAN equipment.

`dateTime`: Timestamp of data record creation.  `Area_Name`: Geographic location of the equipment. `CellId`: Unique identifier of the cell site. `Id2`: Redundant cell site identifier. `Id3`:  Unknown identifier (likely internal). `Id4`: Initial software version identifier. `vsDataType`: Data type indicator. `vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of Ericsson-specific data format. `SwVersion.administrativeData`: Administrative data (currently empty). `SwVersion.userLabel`: User-defined label (currently empty). `SwVersion.timeOfDeactivation`: Timestamp of software deactivation. `SwVersion.consistsOf`:  Detailed composition of the software version, including subnetwork, managed element, and software item IDs. `SwVersion.swVersionId`: Unique software version identifier. `SwVersion.timeOfInstallation`: Timestamp of software installation. `SwVersion.timeOfActivation`: Timestamp of software activation.
